Definition: low tufted perennial phlox with needlelike evergreen leaves and pink or white flowers
Example: native to United States and widely cultivated as a ground cover
Synonyms: mountain_phlox, moss_phlox, dwarf_phlox, Phlox_subulata, phlox, low, tufted, perennial, with, needlelike, evergreen, leaves, and, pink, or, white, flowers, native, to, United, States, widely, cultivated, as, a, ground, cover
Category: noun.plant
